    "body": "Automatically start the difftool when Neovim is launched in diff mode\r\nwith two arguments.\r\n\r\nSigned-off-by: Tomas Slusny <slusnucky@gmail.com>\r\n\r\nUsage: \r\n\r\n```lua\r\nvim.cmd.packadd('nvim.difftool')\r\n```\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnvim -d dir1/ dir2/\r\n```\r\n\r\nOr one liner:\r\n\r\n```\r\nnvim -c \"packadd nvim.difftool\" -d dir1/ dir2/\r\n```\r\n",
