            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "See https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/35448#issuecomment-3957800072 for relevant discussion. Opening as draft for now, as I am not sure if this is best approach with the vim.g config option.\r\n\r\nWill add docs later.\r\n\r\nUsage: \r\n\r\n```lua\r\nvim.cmd.packadd('nvim.difftool')\r\n```\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnvim -d dir1/ dir2/\r\n```\r\n\r\nOr one liner:\r\n\r\n```\r\nnvim -c \"packadd nvim.difftool\" -d dir1/ dir2/\r\n```",
